`opentelemetry-instrumentation-logging`: deprecate camelCase log record attributes (`otelSpanID`, `otelTraceID`, `otelTraceSampled`, `otelServiceName`) in favor of OTel-spec-compliant snake_case names (`span_id`, `trace_id`, `trace_flags`, `service_name`). The old names continue to work and stay in sync with the new ones, but accessing them now emits a `DeprecationWarning`; they will be removed in a future release.
